data.description: Spacious all-brick one level rancher is nestled on nearly 2 beautiful acres. The perfect blend of country living yet conveniently situated between Birmingham and Tuscaloosa and major amenities. If you are looking for a place that you will not soon outgrow, then this is it! This well maintained home features a spacious floor plan boasting new LVP flooring, a large living and dining area that is perfect for entertaining, and each bedroom is generously sized. You will   enjoy hanging out in the Den, a nice second living space with french doors that lead out onto the back deck. If you enjoy the outdoors, this property will not disappoint. There is plenty of space for outdoor fun or to even plant a garden or two! 6-year-old roof and 4-year-old HVAC system help provide peace of mind. No HOA. This wonderful home is now ready for new owners to create cherished memories, just in time for the holiday season!
